title: 🛕 "Just because you make a good plan, doesn't mean that's what's gonna happen." - Taylor Swift
content: is brought to you by Sourcegraph!: Given 10 JavaScript files, write a regular expression script to search the code in all of these files for any private keys or things that look like tokens. The result should return the following: - The name of the file(s) - The line numbers of where the private keys or tokens start and end.
